g.title: j1395965966
g.text: You're free. You can leave. Go anywhere. Anywhere but *here.*

g.title: j3443086511
g.text: We're the past. Dead and gone.

g.title: j2468927541
g.text: Just pieces of a memory or bits of data in one of Amir's games.

g.title: j683782957
g.text: We don't matter anymore. And maybe we never did.

g.title: j2318270756
g.text: Why would you ever keep coming back, when you had the choice to leave?!

g.title: j3194729361
g.text: The pizza is great. So, I like the food?

g.title: j97571225
g.text: For you. For us. For what we have.

g.title: j1390749518
g.text: I don't have time for this. [End.]

g.title: j2115056625
g.text: The pizza is great. So, I like the food?

g.title: j226780466
g.text: If you'd prefer I leave, then just tell me.

g.title: j3066719497
g.text: Do you think I'm just here with you, what, killing time?!

g.title: j2869627929
g.text: Only important person in a world of might-as-well-be-corpses? Charming.

g.title: j4116207151
g.text: Don't put words in my mouth.

g.title: j1652239585
g.text: Arthur. I *care* about you. I care about all the of the Hex, but you most of all.

g.title: j1358335606
g.text: You can do better than that.

g.title: j2173761091
g.text: I like it here. End of story. End of conversation. [End.]

g.title: j565320779
g.text: Why're you so angry at me?

g.title: j3077716264
g.text: I'm sorry I want to be your friend?

g.title: j3539805294
g.text: But it's not a serious question. How could you ask me that?

g.title: j1725144526
g.text: So of *course* I stay here with you!

g.title: j1474031694
g.text: Sol's sake, let that go! And don't change the subject.

g.title: j1955183762
g.text: Stop dodging! Why. Are. You. Still. Here?!

g.title: j3437392059
g.text: You have something I never have. Freedom.

g.title: j3696783354
g.text: It's obvious why I'm here. For *you.* For the Hex. Because you're my family.

g.title: j771951064
g.text: How can you even ask me that?

g.title: j294212363
g.text: Or are we like pets to you? Some sort of sideshow attraction maybe?

g.title: j1137730379
g.text: Because you matter to me more than I can put into words.

g.title: j2897814142
g.text: So I can't leave you behind. This place. This time. With *you?*

g.title: j1814313690
g.text: Because despite the fact it didn't work out between us, I still *care* about you and the rest of the Hex like family.

g.title: j2833268220
g.text: Because I still have feelings for you, that's why!

g.title: j1305863171
g.text: Because I have feelings for you, you ASSHAT.

g.title: j2145526215
g.text: I keep coming back because I...have feelings for you.

g.title: j1086065560
g.text: You want to know why?! Because you're the first FAMILY I've ever had!

g.title: j3540645227
g.text: So what is it? Pity? Or are you stupid as well as crazy?

g.title: j2302482089
g.text: So, no. This place, this time? With *you,* Arthur? This is my home.

g.title: j3834090756
g.text: It's the first place that's ever...felt like home.

g.title: j272376883
g.text: If caring makes me crazy, or stupid, so be it.

g.title: j276752209
g.text: My temper's always been my worst enemy. Let me make it up to you over a pint?

g.title: j443134695
g.text: How can you be telling me this, while you're stringing someone else along?!

g.title: j3988720346
g.text: That's why I keep coming back. Because that's what family *does.*

g.title: j759045594
g.text: I owe you a pint, love. And one of those pizzas.

g.title: j2855553269
g.text: I... sometimes try to find enemies where there aren't any. And I... didn't realize how much we meant to you.

g.title: j1413067075
g.text: How much I meant to you. And that's on me. C'mon. Let's go get a drink.

g.title: j2912152508
g.text: But I owe you an apology, love... And a pint.

g.title: j3942080148
g.text: Yep, sounds just like family to me...

g.title: j293245278
g.text: If you don't tell Eleanor soon, she'll find out on her own.

g.title: j328730711
g.text: After what you've pulled? That won't work on me.

g.title: j3884230604
g.text: But if you want to give this another go, we should talk this though in person.

g.title: j3533729958
g.text: That's all you've got to say?

g.title: j2876524237
g.text: I've got to go think for a bit.

g.title: j1124001844
g.text: For your own safety I'd recommend telling her. But just so you know?

g.title: j1824572896
g.text: You need to tell Amir. It's not fair to him.

g.title: j2000953446
g.text: I accepted you leaving me for the better twin, but... this? There'll be no taking you back.

g.title: j2139613374
g.text: He's got enough to cope with as it is without dealing with your games.

g.title: j2169351166
g.text: Do you know how rare it is for Quincy to trust someone? To really let someone in?

g.title: j2443813156
g.text: No - I mean - I need to go think. I'm sorry.

g.title: Chat ends. Next chat will be ArthurConfession.
g.text: Chat ends. Next chat will be ArthurConfession.

j1607053744
g.text: You're proving all his worst suspicions about the world right.

g.title: j4207465041
g.text: Lettie's supposed to be with someone who helps share the burden.

g.title: j468313309
g.text: Not bloody add to to the pain.
